  <h2 class="section-title">What I built &<br>what I learned</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">Each venture failed in its own way. Each one taught me something the next one needed.</p>

  <div class="ventures-grid">

    <div class="venture-card reveal" style="position:relative; overflow:hidden;">
      <div style="position:absolute; top:1.2rem; right:1.2rem; font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif; font-size:3rem; font-weight:800; color:rgba(249,115,22,0.07); line-height:1; pointer-events:none; user-select:none;">01</div>
